##Module Resposibility Mapping

This document describes the responsibility of each module in the Renewable Energy Prediction System.


Modules Included:--

##Authentication
-User registration
-User login
-User authentication
-User account management


##Solar Prediction
-Process solar data
-Predict solar energy generation
-Store prediction results
-Support solar Analysis


##Wind Prediction
-Process wind data
-Predict wind energy generation
-Store prediction results
-Support wind analysis


##Site suitability
-Analyze Enviromental data
-Calculate suitability score
-Rank sites
-Recommend best locations


##Database
-Store project data
-Manage database tables
-retrive required information
-maintain data integrity


##Reports
-Generate project reports
-Export reports
-Summarize prediction results
-Store report history


##Dashboard
-Display project information
-show prediction results
-Visualize charts and graphs
-Monitor system status


##API Services
-Connect Frontend and Backend
-Handle API requests
-Exchange data between Modules
-Integrate external datasets and services